query:
UPDATE categories SET 
image = CASE WHEN id = 1 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1595777707802-221b42c0bbb2?w=300&h=300&fit=crop'
             WHEN id = 2 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594938298603-c8148c4dae35?w=300&h=300&fit=crop'
             WHEN id = 3 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?w=300&h=300&fit=crop'
             WHEN id = 4 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?w=300&h=300&fit=crop'
             WHEN id = 5 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612336307429-8a88e8d08dbb?w=300&h=300&fit=crop'
             ELSE image
        END;
